title: August 01, 2024 — Support for Streamlit 1.35.0 in Streamlit in Snowflake | Snowflake Documentation
paragraphs:
With this release, we are pleased to announce support for version 1.35.0 of the Streamlit open-source
library in Streamlit in Snowflake.
For more information, see About Streamlit in Snowflake.
